{"tid":1432642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【記者入】唯一對付過期催淚彈方法","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:05:33.000Z","uid":245418,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"774432c26467ac29d25b7bc4baa60dbcac0376b5","tid":1432642,"uid":245418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"記者會問你你唔答吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我懇請各位記者朋友 為咗我地廣大市民嘅健康著想<br />\n當啲黑警下次放催淚彈嘅時候<br />\n麻煩各位<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一人一樽 攞sample去化驗</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有毒冇毒一驗就知<br />\n還POPO清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位 功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be344141cf50def5e9d6eee995f276d55bafa79d","tid":1432642,"uid":221237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"引狗去宿舍附近 俾家人共享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfbea2e8ecbb4ec78c20f41ba421fcd6120c112","tid":1432642,"uid":245418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c55b48ba32b093c5c89231d23a8f9715063e1e3","tid":1432642,"uid":245418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf7d985c6cc637f57f6133c9e2c1fe579d78de8","tid":1432642,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:33:51.000Z","msg":"油站不可打電話"},{"pid":"39f68ed9375f1c1d04fe9b43d0353d62546f9cae","tid":1432642,"uid":245418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"